  "prompt": "How do I hire a truck in Bangalore?",
  "response": "To hire a truck in Bangalore, you can follow these steps:\n\n1. Online Platforms\n\u2022 Truck Booking Apps\n- Blackbuck\n- Freight Tiger\n- Lobb\n- Porter\n\n2. Local Transport Agents\n\u2022 Contact local transport agents in areas like:\n- Majestic\n- Yeshwanthpur\n- Rajajinagar\n- KR Market\n\n3. Transportation Websites\n\u2022 99trucks.com\n\u2022 Trucksuvidha.com\n\u2022 Transporters.in\n\n4. Required Information/Documents\n\u2022 Your pickup and drop location\n\u2022 Type of truck needed\n\u2022 Load weight\n\u2022 Distance to be covered\n\u2022 Your contact details\n\u2022 Valid ID proof\n\u2022 Driver's license\n\n5. Local Truck Unions/Associations\n\u2022 Contact truck unions for reliable options\n\u2022 Get recommendations from local transporters\n\n6. Truck Types Available\n\u2022 Tempo/Mini truck\n\u2022 7-9 feet truck\n\u2022 14-17 feet truck\n\u2022 20-32 feet truck\n\u2022 Open/Closed body trucks\n\n7. Pricing Factors\n\u2022 Distance\n\u2022 Load weight\n\u2022 Truck type\n\u2022 Fuel charges\n\u2022 Loading/unloading charges\n\nRecommended to compare rates and verify truck condition before hiring.",
